{% extends 'template/layout_en_content.twig' %}
{% block content %}
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <img src="{{ base_url() }}/assets/img/pages/services-ma.jpg" width="100%" alt="" />
            <p>&nbsp;</p>
            <h4>Transactions</h4>
            <p>
                <strong>M&A Advisory</strong>
            </p>
            <p>
                We support our clients with their M&A needs on both the sell side and buy
                                      side. A key component of both is the valuation and assessment process. As
                                      seasoned professionals, we possess the expertise to identify and evaluate
                                      the key financial and operational drivers. Additionally, we leverage
                                      industry knowledge with experience in audit, legal, regulatory and
                                      investor communities. This ensures our clients have the right information
                                      to clearly assess their decisions at various points during the process.
            </p>
            <p>Our sell side services include:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    Pre-sale due diligence to assess risks and market potential to
                                                best position and prepare the company for the sale process
                </li>
                <li>
                    Assessing the best way in which to structure the sale to maximize
                                                proceeds, manage tax exposures and minimize counter party risks
                </li>
                <li>
                    Assessing value considerations and the implications to the capital
                                                structure
                </li>
                <li>
                    Active and early input into the identification of key deal issues that
                                                feed into the transaction documents, including the sale and purchase
                                                agreements, shareholders agreements, transition services agreements and
                                                supply agreements
                </li>
                <li>
                    Managing the disclosure of sensitive corporate data and preparation of
                                                data rooms
                </li>
                <li>
                    Negotiating key terms and covenants with potential buyers, as well as
                                                managing the execution and closing process
                </li>
                <li>Organizing and coordinating supporting professionals</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Our buy-side services include:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    Buy-side financial and commercial due diligence to assess risks and
                                                value potential to best position and prepare the company for the
                                                negotiation process and the impact of the acquisition
                </li>
                <li>
                    Assessing the best way in which to structure and fund the acquisition,
                                                manage tax exposures and minimize counter party risks
                </li>
                <li>
                    Preparing projections and assessing the value of the transaction
                                                relative to the companyâ€™s market valuation and the impact on its capital
                                                structure
                </li>
                <li>
                    Active and early input into the identification of key deal issues that
                                                feed into the transaction documents, including the sale and purchase
                                                agreements, shareholders agreements, transition services agreements and
                                                supply agreements
                </li>
                <li>Collecting, interpreting and assessing sensitive corporate data</li>
                <li>
                    Negotiating key terms and covenants with potential buyers, as well as
                                                managing the execution and closing process
                </li>
                <li>Organizing and coordinating supporting professionals</li>
                <li>
                    Supporting and dealing with the regulators and the stock exchange as
                                                necessary (for public companies)
                </li>
            </ul>
            <p>
                <strong>Fund Raising</strong>
            </p>
            <p>
                We assist our clients evaluate their funding needs, identify the right
                                      sources and raise the necessary funds throughout the capital structure,
                                      ranging from working capital funding and senior secured term debt to
                                      subordinated or unsecured debt and equity capital.
            </p>
            <p>Our services include:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Providing expert advice on capital structuring</li>
                <li>
                    Raising funds from commercial banks, investment banks, private equity
                                                funds, alternative capital providers or strategic investors
                </li>
                <li>
                    Creating information circulars and other marketing materials to properly
                                                position your company and create the right level of interest
                </li>
                <li>
                    Negotiating key terms and covenants with potential funders, as well as
                                                negotiating inter-creditor agreements
                </li>
                <li>
                    Managing the execution and closing process to secure financing and
                                                maximize future value
                </li>
            </ul>
            <p>&nbsp;</p>
            <div class="row" id="nav-case-study">
                {% for data in page.data %}
                    {% if data.TypeofCase == page.service %}
                        <div class="card" style="width: 25rem;margin: 12px;">
                            <div class="card-body">
                                <div class="title-case">
                                    <span style="font-size:10px;float:left;margin-top:15px;">Case Study</span>
                                    <span><img alt="" src="{{ base_url() }}/assets/img/logo/logo-landing-transparent-sm.png" style="float: right;margin-top: 0px;" width="70px" /></span>
                                </div>
                                <h5 class="card-title" style="margin-top:80px;margin-bottom: 0px;">
                                    {{ data.header }}
                                </h5>
                                <span style="font-size: 10px;">{{ data.DateofClosing }}</span><br/><br/>
                                <p style="margin-top:20px;">
                                    <span style="margin-top: 40px;">
                                        <a href="{{ base_url() }}/EN/services/{{ page.service }}/{{ data.id }}#nav-case-study" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-sm">Read More</a>
                                    </span>
                                    <span class="sc-box-value">{{
                                data.Value
                              }}</span>
                                </p>
                                <span class="sc-box-value-saying">{{
                              data.Saying
                            }}</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    {% endif %}
                {% endfor %}
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <p class="pages-content">&nbsp;</p>
{% endblock %}